gomodel:SYNGO_4966  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1a-b: authors developed an assay to image the surface expressed pool of mGluR5 (GRM5) in live cells and observe agonist-induced mGluR5 internalization in dendritic spines of hippocampal neurons.\n\nFigure 1c-d: internalized mGluR5 puncta overlapped with the lysosomal marker GFP-LAMP1 (LAMP1: 31% ± 5%). Experimental description: M&M: \"Hippocampal cultures were prepared from embryonic day 18 (E18) Janvier Wistar rat brains (both genders) as described in Cunha-Ferreira et al. (2018).\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2023-02-03" ;
